Plan for iteration 10 (`ScorerSet`):
1. Add `src/scorer_set.rs` with a public builder API matching the spec example: `builder()`, optional `.map_output()`, optional `.map_reference()`, one-or-more `.scorer()`, then `.build()`.
2. Keep the public API minimal and spec-aligned; use an internal type-erased scorer adapter so the set can store heterogeneous async scorers despite `Scorer` not being object-safe.
